reviewText: What a blast! Not one of "Baseball's Greatest Games" by any means, just a trip back in a time machine to watch an ordinary Saturday afternoon regular-season game 40 years ago. (No "modern" intrusions--this is simply a tape from Armed Forces TV of the game, uncut) From the groovy opening credit sequence to the Tony Kubek interview with Leo the Lip after the game...if you like your nostalgia straight up, then this is definitely for you.
